## ğŸ” Discovery Commands

*Use these commands to discover model relationships:*

### Find All Models

```bash
find app/Models -name '*.php' -type f
```

### Count Models by Namespace

```bash
find app/Models -name '*.php' -type f | \
  xargs -I {} dirname {} | \
  sort | uniq -c
```

### Find Models Using HasOrganization

```bash
grep -r "use HasOrganization" app/Models | wc -l
```

### Find Models Extending BaseModel

```bash
grep -r "extends BaseModel" app/Models | wc -l
```

### Find Polymorphic Relationships

```bash
grep -r "morphTo\|morphMany\|morphOne" app/Models
```
